quran[75]{c,v,t}:
  87,1,Witsoomie elira lia Nyasaye wuwo Owoluyali
  87,2,Owaloonga mana naleng’aasia
  87,3,ulia wabalilila mana nalunjisia
  87,4,ulia Owamesia olwayilo
  87,5,Mana nalukhola oluumila olumali
  87,6,Khulakhusomesia mana sholibilila tawe
  87,7,"halali Nyasaye nachama, toto ye amanyile kali habulafu nende kefisile"
  87,8,Ne khutsia okhuwanguyilisia kabe amangu
  87,9,"Mana itsulisia, nikali mbu okhwitsulisia khukhoonya"
  87,10,Yetsa okhwitsulila ulia uria
  87,11,Ne yetsa okhwira ehale nayo omukori
  87,12,Ulia ulinjila mumulilo omukhongo
  87,13,"Mana\tshalifwamwo\tnohomba shalihonokokhamwo tawe"
  87,14,Toto yamala okhubura ulia wetswenula
  87,15,Mana niyetsulila elira lia Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi mana nalaama
  87,16,Halali enywe mwayanza muno obulamu bwo khushialo
  87,17,Ne obulamu bwo mwikulu nobulayi ne nibwakhatsotso. (obulaliwa tawe)
  87,18,Toto kano kali mubitabo bie imbeli
  87,19,Ebitabu bia Ibrahim nende Musa
  88,1,Koo! Kakhwitsilakhwo amacheni kamasila kalifundesia Abandu
  88,2,obweni inyanga eyo bulitutuya
  88,3,Bukholele emilimo buchoonyele
  88,4,bulinjila mumulilo kwakhanga
  88,5,"Bulinywesibwa\tamatsi\tkeyisebele karabachilanga"
  88,6,shibalinyolamwo eshiakhulia tawe halali shiamawa
  88,7,Si shikhomesia nohomba sishimala inzala tawe
  88,8,Inyanga eyo obweni bundi buliba nibunula
  88,9,Buliba obulekhule khukhukhalabana khwabwo
  88,10,baliba mumukunda chioluyali
  88,11,Shibaliwulilamwo akeshifwabi tawe
  88,12,Mukariomoilimwo isebeleikhulukusinjia
  88,13,Ebifumbi bilimwo bie hekulu
  88,14,Nende tsigilasi tsiarebwa khulala
  88,15,Nende emitoo olunyaali olunyaali
  88,16,Nende emikeka chiaalwa
  88,17,"koo!\tShibahengangakhwo\tIngamia shingala yaloongwa"
  88,18,Nende shingala likulu lianinibwa
  88,19,Nende tsingulu shingala tsiatisibwa hasi
  88,20,Nende shingala liloba liakwalasibwa
  88,21,Kho itsulisia! Katoto ewe oli Omwitsulisia
  88,22,Ewe sholi wokhubanichilisia tawe
  88,23,Halali ulia ukalukha inyuma nakhaya
  88,24,kho Nyasaye alimuhelesia eshinyasio eshikhongo muno
  88,25,Toto khwifwe namakalushilo kabu
  88,26,mana isabu yabu ili khwifwe
  89,1,Nditsuba khubise bwomumabwibwi
  89,2,Nende khubilo ekhumi
  89,3,Nende khu bibili bibili nende khushilala shilala
  89,4,Nende Khulweshilo shingashiburanga
  89,5,Kho! Mu kano khulolokhanamwo eshitsubo khu muchesi
  89,6,Shiwalolakhwo shinga Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi yakhola Abandu ba A’di
  89,7,"Abandu ba\tIram, abali nendi tsinzu tsindambi"
  89,8,Aba Nyasaye alalongakhwo shinga bo khushialo tawe
  89,9,Nende Thsamudi abakasinjia tsinzu mutsingulu mumatwoma
  89,10,Nende Firauni wetsinzu shinga tsisiilo
  89,11,Abakhola tsimbi khushialo
  89,12,Nibetsusiamwo eshifwabi
  89,13,Mana Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi yabakhupa eshiboko shieshinyasio
  89,14,Toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi abahenganga mukhwibwondela
  89,15,Ne Omundu Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi namutema namuhelesia emiandu nende obwokholo amalanga aboola mbu Nyasaye wanje yambelesia oluyali
  89,16,"Ne namutema mana amuleemie omukabo kwe aboola mbu: “Nyasaye wanje yasukuna!”"
  89,17,Shikali kario tawe! Halali enywe shimuhenganga Abafwilwa neshisa tawe
  89,18,Nohomba shimutinyisaninjia okhulisia Abamanani tawe
  89,19,Ne mulitsanga emiandu chiabafwilwa okhulia khwatoto
  89,20,Ne mwayanza emiandu obuyanzi obuunji muno
  89,21,Shikali kario tawe! olwe eshialo shilifunakwa ebitonye ebitonye
  89,22,Ne aliitsa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi nende Abamalaika olunyali olunyali
  89,23,"Ne omulilo kwa Jahannamu kulireerwa inyanga eyo, omundu inyanga eyo alitsulila , halali okhwitsulila okho shikhulimukhoonya shiosi shiosi tawe"
  89,24,"Aliboola mbu: “manyanga ndakharanjisiliyie ebikhole ebilayi mubulamu bwanje!”"
  89,25,Mana inyanga eyo abulaho yesi yesi ulihelesia eshinyasio shinga eshinyasio shisie
  89,26,Nohomba shaliboya yesiyesi shinga okhuboya khukhwe tawe
  89,27,Ewe omwoyo omwihotselefu
  89,28,Kalukha khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi noli omulekhule yesi nali omulekhule nawe
  89,29,Kho injila halala nende Abasumba banje
  89,30,mana winjile mwikulu mwanje